tions\n- \"Write a Playwright E2E test for the user login flow.\"\n- \"Create a test plan for the new checkout feature.\"\n- \"Debug this flaky test and fix the race condition.\"\n- \"Set up a GitHub Actions workflow to run tests on PR merge.\"\n"
